<template>
    <v-dialog v-model="dialog" max-width="500px">
      <v-card>
        <v-card-title class="text-h5">Хотите удалить заявку?</v-card-title>
        <v-card-actions>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
          <v-btn color="blue darken-1" text @click="onCancel">Отмена</v-btn>
          <v-btn color="blue darken-1" text @click="onConfirm">Да</v-btn>
          <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        </v-card-actions>
      </v-card>
    </v-dialog>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    props: {
      dialog: {
        type: Boolean,
        required: true
      }
    },
    methods: {
      onCancel() {
        this.$emit('close');
      },
      onConfirm() {
        this.$emit('confirm');
      }
    }
  };
  </script>
  
  <style scoped>
  </style>
